reviewText: Shipping was quick and easy. Everything arrived as promised and both of the movies are fantastic! A great purchase for anyone!
The 5 stars are for Master & Commander. The authentic feel of the scenery and acting are unparalleled.
Two great stories about big adventure, honor and duty.  Both are well done, cast perfectly and well written.  Truely enjoyable

Loved the Kingdom of heaven for its humanity.
Master and Commander, the music added so much more depth to the strong characters.
Enjoyed them both immensely.

Both of these movies were great and worth the $$$. I especially liked Master & Commander, but then I'm a great Russel Crowe fan! The pictures and sound were great and I would recommend this DVD to anyone. Two great movies for less than the price of one!
two good movies not to miss at all with lot of insights in both of them,i did really enjoy them.
Two movies that are good, historically accurate(lifestyle wise) yet entirely fictional movies.
Two of my favorite movies, great to travel with.
DVD casing was broken upon receipt, but the DVDs were unscathed and a treat to watch
I don't remember Master and Commander being a very popular movie, I wanted to see it, ordered it and think it excellent. Kingdom of Heaven to me was simply epic.
Kingdom of heaven was a good movie, but Master and commander was terrible.
love it when you have combo packs of movies....
